Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你亲热\N想要好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在想像着肉棒插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边打手枪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛露出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看清楚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸吗？\N继续摸,不要停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想拉起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋起来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡进去很舒服的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗？\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴好酥麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续磨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像着用你的肉棒磨蹭我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好想像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒在这里磨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨到小豆豆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这根也要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边想像着一边打手枪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小豆豆被刺激着很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不能射喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我越来越湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒磨蹭着爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越来越爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被磨蹭太爽了\N爽到要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好湿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到湿湿的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到小豆豆涨起来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩这根吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是透明的,看到我的淫穴了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这根玩意都湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这根是你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要停,继续磨蹭我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张开给我看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的肉棒\N让我爽之后的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听见有多强的震感吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放进去的话一定会更爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要更爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要继续按摩,要更爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有这根\N这根吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有很多玩具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顶到淫穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样磨好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:19:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有够震的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要陪我高潮去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我很爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你的肉棒弄得很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要继续享受喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家已经湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很累耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快给人家肉棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能再睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭臭的好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.10,0:23:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.05,0:24:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家要享受
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.77,0:25:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.77,0:25:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来了？\N你到底在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.11,0:26:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.38,0:26:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快让我爽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.73,0:26:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.82,0:26:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.89,0:27:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舌头伸出来舔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.12,0:27:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.78,0:28:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.67,0:28:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想干我了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.34,0:29:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舔我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.69,0:29:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.10,0:29:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒磨着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.17,0:29:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了吧\N我还想要
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.31,0:29:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你起来\N干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.25,0:29:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骑上去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.93,0:29:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.18,0:30:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好硬喔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.99,0:30:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越来越爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.14,0:32:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.00,0:32:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要爽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.81,0:32:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.92,0:33:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒插进来好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.23,0:33:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插得好深
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.62,0:34:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续给我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.67,0:35:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.88,0:35:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉,顶到最深处了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.89,0:37:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.38,0:38:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽到一直高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.97,0:40:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.91,0:40:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整根插进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.12,0:40:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以用力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.52,0:40:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以继续磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.72,0:40:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要好好享受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.68,0:41:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快插进去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.17,0:41:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有够爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.28,0:42:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太淫荡了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.30,0:42:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了,可以高潮吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.79,0:43:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.27,0:43:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.23,0:44:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.96,0:44:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要继续磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.14,0:45:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.24,0:46:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小豆豆好酥麻喔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.59,0:46:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再插进来,插深点
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.88,0:46:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.43,0:47:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.36,0:47:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用力干我,让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.53,0:47:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.05,0:48:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒好猛喔,射给我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.12,0:48:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都射给我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.53,0:48:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.90,0:49:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都射了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.38,0:49:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在嘴巴里
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.76,0:50:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.30,0:50:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要磨蹭我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.39,0:50:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒硬了吗？\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.78,0:51:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你更硬
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.83,0:52:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.77,0:52:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整根肉棒包住了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.38,0:53:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.20,0:53:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.03,0:53:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夹住了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.90,0:53:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道是什么夹住你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.97,0:53:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒挺前来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.77,0:54:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.54,0:54:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.89,0:54:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夹住了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.51,0:55:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨蹭着小穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.47,0:55:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的奶也在晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.23,0:56:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.85,0:56:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来\N真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.66,0:56:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错,就是这
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.56,0:57:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好紧\N感觉到紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.97,0:57:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用力磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.44,0:57:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.12,0:57:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续干我
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.34,0:57:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.48,0:58:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在干我的小穴\N感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.75,0:58:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到湿湿的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.89,0:58:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的小穴很湿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.96,0:58:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插得好用力
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.85,0:58:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干我爽吗？\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.79,0:58:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的淫汁
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.66,0:58:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你干到淫汁不停流出来
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.14,0:58:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.55,0:59:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.44,0:59:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.66,0:59:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.81,1:00:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才真的是在干淫穴吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.88,1:00:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么,感觉不到很湿吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.96,1:00:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那触感...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.16,1:00:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.83,1:00:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实你只是在干丝袜而已
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.04,1:00:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会...\N不过也很爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.12,1:00:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.79,1:01:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你继续磨我
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.93,1:01:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.47,1:01:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才磨蹭我爽吗？\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.10,1:01:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.85,1:01:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.31,1:01:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我的淫穴更爽
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.41,1:02:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨蹭好兴奋哦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.81,1:02:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁眼也磨到了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.50,1:02:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.05,1:03:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在用力点磨
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.72,1:03:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力点
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.62,1:03:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.49,1:03:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.12,1:04:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽到快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.60,1:04:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.29,1:04:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用力啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.91,1:05:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.91,1:05:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着换我主动了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.22,1:05:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.63,1:06:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样磨很爽\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.97,1:06:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到肉棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.71,1:06:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.27,1:06:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到我的淫穴吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.22,1:07:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要快一点
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.82,1:07:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要和我一起高潮
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.84,1:07:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.41,1:07:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.82,1:08:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有耶
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.36,1:08:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还有？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.50,1:08:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.50,1:08:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.17,1:08:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴磨蹭很爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.37,1:08:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞到这么远了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.64,1:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体都沾到了\N好淫荡
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.32,1:08:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨蹭我的小穴爽吗\N爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.13,1:08:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.07,1:08:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.54,1:09:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再一起玩
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.09,1:09:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有哪里痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.56,1:09:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不痛了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.50,1:09:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？我帮你看一下伤口
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.18,1:09:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该能看得看吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.78,1:09:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.76,1:10:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,有点长
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.83,1:10:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没拆好
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.90,1:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.99,1:10:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.99,1:11:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没好？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.73,1:11:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.94,1:11:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么味道？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.41,1:11:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淫荡的味道\N你说什么,快吃掉
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.95,1:11:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别欺负我了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.56,1:11:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快帮我拆\N现在说是医生
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.90,1:11:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我看不见\N等一下也不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.37,1:11:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你拆,但有条件
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.91,1:11:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.45,1:12:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.86,1:12:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你肉棒硬了,\N就代表你看得见了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.40,1:12:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒硬了你就能出院了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.82,1:12:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.76,1:12:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不见吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.50,1:12:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底看不看得见？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.79,1:14:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把肉棒掏出来,\N这里是医院耶
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.99,1:14:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是医生你...\N别这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.47,1:14:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.07,1:14:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.88,1:14:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还硬撑、成这样
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.95,1:14:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么自己把肉棒掏出来
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.24,1:15:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.31,1:15:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是医院耶
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.39,1:15:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢我用脚吗\N喜欢...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.54,1:15:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这根不够爽
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.34,1:15:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.95,1:15:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把肉棒放在桌上
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.50,1:17:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被看见就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.63,1:17:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.87,1:17:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉哦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.74,1:17:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是硬硬的比较爽
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.74,1:17:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被看见就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.28,1:18:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要快一点
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.23,1:18:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们最后要一起高潮
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.22,1:19:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边打手枪一边磨蹭\N快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.30,1:19:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去吗\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.01,1:20:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.68,1:20:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我流汗了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.55,1:20:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我擦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.22,1:20:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擦？\N嗯,用肉棒擦干净
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.77,1:20:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好的擦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.20,1:21:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗？\N很爽
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.67,1:21:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想射了吗\N快了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.55,1:21:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能射在这
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.68,1:21:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不给你射
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.75,1:21:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会弄脏我的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.63,1:24:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.97,1:25:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.21,1:25:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射好多喔
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.22,1:25:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有够多的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.23,1:26:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢医生
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.10,1:26:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.90,1:26:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢医生,我很爽\N你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.91,1:26:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是医院,什么很爽？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.85,1:26:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是风俗店,\N你要检查脑袋吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.66,1:26:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把你转去脑科,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.60,1:26:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你检查清楚脑袋
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.98,1:28:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.13,1:28:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨蹭小穴太赞了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.61,1:29:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬硬的太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.11,1:30:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要继续磨
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.93,1:31:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒夹住了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.68,1:31:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样爽吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.10,1:31:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插进来
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.57,1:31:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再快点
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.61,1:32:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒一直在抖动
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.73,1:33:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨蹭着小豆豆
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.54,1:35:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还想高潮
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.14,1:35:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续给我磨
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.95,1:35:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会让你们爽的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.51,1:36:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨蹭里面好爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.44,1:37:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.54,1:37:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉哦
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.48,1:38:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒在插深点
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.21,1:39:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.63,1:40:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力点
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.23,1:40:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.52,1:40:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着磨蹭我
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.86,1:41:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.73,1:42:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好深好爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.54,1:42:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磨吧,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.09,1:42:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.35,1:43:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续磨蹭我
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.03,1:43:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒插进来磨
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.98,1:44:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插入了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.93,1:44:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在里面磨蹭好有感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.43,1:46:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续给我
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.79,1:46:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁眼好爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.25,1:48:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽死我了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.99,1:48:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.60,1:48:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这姿势看得好清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.22,1:50:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快射了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.49,1:50:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要尽情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.49,1:50:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续抽送,射多点
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.90,1:51:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要给我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:51:47.37,1:51:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要磨蹭我哦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.85,1:52:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淫汁流出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.60,1:53:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插得好快,不停的在里面磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.76,1:53:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽到受不了了...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.63,1:53:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.57,1:54:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.84,1:54:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射给我
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.10,1:55:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.40,1:55:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面外面都好舒服喔

